\newlabel{tab:tau_scaling}{{7}{8}{$\tau ^*$ scaling law validation. For $L\ge 1024$ the prediction matches well; at short $L$ the measured optimum is systematically higher (PE-dominant regime where model capacity is the bottleneck)}{table.7}{}}
